{"tid":1958744,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"關於賣車問題","createTime":"2020-04-05T01:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T06:46:39.000Z","uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d96f04a882725b6c276d245018ad48876a7a7f66","tid":1958744,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩賣車，對方即刻就要俾cash<br />\n寫左張紙話全數已收<br />\n<br />\n但問題就黎啦，佢用緊我份保險，我聽日打去cut <br />\n但有咩事會唔會入我數？另外我見到佢賣緊我架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢依加用我名義賣架車，會唔會有問題？<br />\n佢一直唔過戶就一直用緊我個名，抄牌果啲咪一直寄俾我？ 如果佢真係唔過我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟第一次賣車，真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRwinU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRwinU6.png&h=78b41390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b57a9e44dcbbc25a0822e5400b2e7f80c912409","tid":1958744,"uid":26766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"你份買賣合約無寫明等過戶其間唔郁得車？有無抄低里數？"},{"pid":"2804980f9b9968a53e5fe413cf43aa819a0997ef","tid":1958744,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"我仲有條後備車匙未俾佢<br />\n<br />\n仲可以叫佢出黎一次<br />\n<br />\n佢轉手賺到錢係佢本事，最驚係遇到騙徒<br />\n手法層出不窮，呃人地落訂然後唔交車？<br />\n然後咪入我數？我淨係諗到呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c07e5461373a6e6fbc8e19c208e624c60a89d0f","tid":1958744,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b57a9e44dcbbc25a0822e5400b2e7f80c912409","tid":1958744,"uid":26766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"你份買賣合約無寫明等過戶其間唔郁得車？有無抄低里數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"淨係寫左呢張紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji